### Validation of Clinical Findings

**Primary survey reliability:**
\`\`\`
Finding               Sensitivity  Specificity  Use Case
Absent radial pulse   ~85% for SBP<80  ~95%    Severe hypotension
Altered mental status ~70% for shock   Variable Perfusion marker
Cap refill >2s        ~50% for shock   ~80%    Nonspecific
Tachycardia           ~60% for hypovolemia ~50% Early indicator
